Parmalat Board to Meet May 3 on Lactalis Offer, Sole Says

-- B y   T o m m a s o   E b h a r d t
-- 
2011-04-30T10:02:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-30/parmalat-board-to-meet-may-3-on-lactalis-offer-sole-says.html
Parmalat SpA (PLT) ’s board will meet May
3 to evaluate Groupe Lactalis’s 3.4 billion-euro ($5 billion)
offer for  Italy ’s biggest dairy company, Il Sole 24 Ore
reported, without saying where it got the information.  Parmalat may select an adviser to provide a fairness
opinion on the bid, the Italian newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tommaso Ebhardt in Milan at 
 tebhardt@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chad Thomas at   cthomas16@bloomberg.net . 